      <title>CLP将资本集中在香港和中国的清洁能力推向上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/clp-to-focus-capital-on-hong-kong-and-china-in-clean-power-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CLP Holdings Ltd.计划专注于在香港和中国大陆上进行投资，而其他地区的项目则需要自筹资金，因为该公用事业公司寻求更绿色的发电投资组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/clp-to-focus-capital-on-hong-kong-and-china-in-clean-power-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 02:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
